Deploy AMW to Openshift
-----------------------

Preconditions:
--------------
POD:

AMW is deployed to OpenShift via the tool

checkout
git clone https://github.com/puzzle/puzzle-openshift-tool.git

set the correct path to the deploy script in createanddeploy.sh POT_HOME

RHC:
* Install Ruby
* for ubuntu sudo apt-get install ruby1.9.1
* sudo gem install rhc
* configure rhc to use your openShift installation in our case broker.openshift-dev.puzzle.ch
** rhc setup

Deployment
----------

cd ../
mvn clean install
cd ../AMW_openshift
./createanddeploy.sh <user>


the createanddeploy.sh also creates a new application Instanz



